{"tid":2501675,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"舞台設計男生藏電筒脫罪  官指警截查武斷 問基礎何在","createTime":"2021-04-23T14:18:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T14:18:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a6ad3a0037d03d37f2311d4b01bb5ad9010a0eae","tid":2501675,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T14:18:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210423/GNNZ6NND7BCMZJ3HESB5YQBK7U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210423%2FGNNZ6NND7BCMZJ3HESB5YQBK7U%2F&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzn0iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=446a30ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210423%2FGNNZ6NND7BCMZJ3HESB5YQBK7U%2F&h=0d0fef85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210423/GNNZ6NND7BCMZJ3HESB5YQBK7U/</a><br />\n<br />\n舞台設計男生藏電筒脫罪 <br />\n官指警截查武斷 問基礎何在<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年2月市民「和你Lunch」紀念元朗7.21事件七個月，一名西九文化區舞台設計實習生在附近非示威位置遭截查，搜出17吋長電筒。舞台工早前就管有攻擊性武器控罪受審，辯稱電筒為舞台工作所需。案件昨裁決，裁判官指警員看見有人揮動美國國旗後一小時始看見被告，因懷疑被告有份揮旗而截查，質疑警員截查決定武斷及「基礎何在」；控方舉證亦反駁不到被告因工帶電筒的說法，裁定罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n被告江祈璋（26歲）被控去年2月21日在九龍灣MegaBox商場外管有攻擊性武器或其他適合作非法用途的工具。他昨散庭後表示鬆一口氣，形容警方濫捕，「本身唔喺衝突現場，根本唔應該隨便搜身」。他鼓勵在囚手足「頂住，會還公義畀你哋」。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官屈麗雯昨指，警員19751陳偉倫（譯音）。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n屈官續指，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cJ5Y8w6Fq3LgJ7cDWBjjeYP-3vU=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JGSVBZ7HSNESDESOYX42LOOLXQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcJ5Y8w6Fq3LgJ7cDWBjjeYP-3vU%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJGSVBZ7HSNESDESOYX42LOOLXQ.jpg&h=0222d63f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告江祈璋（右）昨獲判無罪，散庭時形容警方濫捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n控方無安排專家檢驗電筒<br />\n<br />\n至於涉案電筒，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n律政司將本案主控工作外聘予曾在其他審訊激昂撐警、被揭在facebook發表大量「藍絲」偏頗言論的大律師陳文慧處理。陳在盤問本案舞台工時，質疑被告稱集會與網上聯署邀請美國專家來港協助抗疫，說法純屬虛構，反問：「點解要搵美國幫手抗疫？最渣係佢，全世界！佢好叻咩？」<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KTCC1443/20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HYEcbOYT-MYX240WhQsfTDn54o0=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PKIIQJ7Y6JFFFBPNFEO3KIHH74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHYEcbOYT-MYX240WhQsfTDn54o0%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPKIIQJ7Y6JFFFBPNFEO3KIHH74.jpg&h=a1bcfe71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警員19751陳偉倫曾截查被告，被質疑欠缺基礎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/I77GfM_OVxCNT-RhcPGf7kiEFJg=/510x359/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IDMX2JDXW5AINNUNF7QJXHQEAA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FI77GfM_OVxCNT-RhcPGf7kiEFJg%3D%2F510x359%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIDMX2JDXW5AINNUNF7QJXHQEAA.jpg&h=00c6e1f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■外聘主控陳文慧未能反駁被告辯解。"}]}